\u0131<\/li>\n<li>\u0130\u015f kazalar\u0131n\u0131n tespiti ve \u00f6nlenmesi<\/li>\n<li>Personel ve vardiya takibi<\/li>\n<li>Hukuki s\u00fcre\u00e7lerde delil olu\u015fturma<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0130stanbul\u2019daki yo\u011fun lojistik hareketlilik, bu ihtiyac\u0131 daha da art\u0131rmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h2>End\u00fcstriyel Alanlar \u0130\u00e7in Kamera T\u00fcrleri<\/h2>\n<h3>IP End\u00fcstriyel Kameralar<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Y\u00fcksek \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcn\u00fcrl\u00fck (Full HD \u2013 4K)<\/li>\n<li>Geni\u015f alan kapsama<\/li>\n<li>Uzaktan merkezi izleme<\/li>\n<li>Yapay zek\u00e2 destekli analizler<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>B\u00fcy\u00fck depo ve fabrikalar i\u00e7in IP kameralar en ideal \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmd\u00fcr.<\/p>\n<h3>PTZ (Hareketli) Kameralar<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>360\u00b0 d\u00f6nebilme<\/li>\n<li>Zoom ile detayl\u0131 izleme<\/li>\n<li>Geni\u015f sahalar\u0131n tek kamerayla kontrol\u00fc<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Y\u00fcksek tavanl\u0131 ve a\u00e7\u0131k alanlar i\u00e7in tercih edilir.<\/p>\n<h3>Termal Kameralar<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>D\u00fc\u015f\u00fck \u0131\u015f\u0131k ve zorlu ko\u015fullarda alg\u0131lama<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7evre g\u00fcvenli\u011fi<\/li>\n<li>Yang\u0131n riski tespiti<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0130stanbul\u2019daki kritik sanayi tesislerinde yayg\u0131nla\u015fmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h2>Depo ve Fabrikalarda Kamera Konumland\u0131rma<\/h2>\n<p>Profesyonel konumland\u0131rma, sistemin ba\u015far\u0131s\u0131n\u0131 do\u011frudan etkiler:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ana giri\u015f ve \u00e7\u0131k\u0131\u015flar<\/li>\n<li>Y\u00fckleme rampalar\u0131<\/li>\n<li>Stok alanlar\u0131<\/li>\n<li>\u00dcretim hatlar\u0131<\/li>\n<li>D\u0131\u015f \u00e7evre ve \u00e7it hatt\u0131<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Nexus G\u00fcvenlik, \u0130stanbul\u2019daki projelerde detayl\u0131 ke\u015fif ile k\u00f6r noktalar\u0131 tamamen ortadan kald\u0131r\u0131r.<\/p>\n<hr \/>\n<h2>Zorlu \u00c7evre Ko\u015fullar\u0131 \u0130\u00e7in Dayan\u0131kl\u0131 Sistemler<\/h2>\n<p>End\u00f